    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-80af-bca2-fb67940f0d26",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors present DESPRO, a method meant to identify the roles being played by different members in a team. The method uses network analysis to “identify” different roles in collaborative settings. The authors present their framework, followed by a case-study.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
